{"tid":910502,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[強國日常] 鼻插喉強灌水半日增重　牛隻受苦痛極流淚","createTime":"2018-11-21T08:38:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-23T07:53:31.000Z","uid":75969,"like":12,"dislike":214,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"fa0fe089d59da29d127c33eaa43bc22e162701c3","tid":910502,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T08:38:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20181121/photo/bkn-20181121111013931-1121_00952_001_01p.jpg?20181121120641\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20181121%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181121111013931-1121_00952_001_01p.jpg%3F20181121120641&h=fb47fd30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地媒體近日調查後發現，安徽滁州有兩處黑心屠場，為將牛肉賣得更高價錢，宰牛前12小時將重60公斤的水強注入牛隻體內，令牛隻增重。牛隻每晚受盡折磨，有牛牛更不禁落下「牛眼淚」，令人慘不忍睹。惟屠場老闆稱，牛隻反正要被屠宰，灌水之事沒甚麼大不了。<br />\n<br />\n從其中一處屠場所見，幾隻牛的鼻孔都插了膠水管，不停灌水。牛隻表現痛苦，不斷「大吐苦水」。屠夫為防牛隻吐出灌水，用木塞封堵膠水管，逼牛隻強吞下去。多隻牛均身形浮腫，腹部被水灌至圓滾滾的漲起，慘無人道。其中一隻牛疑因承受不住，跪在地上，哀叫之餘還流下眼淚。居於屠宰場附近的居民指，每晚都聽到牛隻的哀鳴聲，可見晚晚都有大量牛隻受苦。<br />\n<br />\n有屠場工人指，他們每天早上7點開始注水工作，歷時12小時。另有工人表示，他們都認為行為殘忍，但工作所在，惟有照做。屠場老闆許男指，牛隻入得屠場都是要被宰殺，即使沒注水，亦難逃一死。不過許男指，給牛注水其實沒增加多少重量。<br />\n<br />\n由於該兩個屠場的牛肉均銷往南京巿，記者遂向南京巿公安局食品藥品環境犯罪偵查支隊舉報。該支隊上周五（16日）聯同警方，分赴該兩個屠場突擊搜查，繳獲13隻活牛，並查獲6隻已屠宰的注水牛，共拘捕29人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20181121/bkn-20181121111013931-1121_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20181121%2Fbkn-20181121111013931-1121_00952_001.html&d=RX7ZHns07AflqApY6FlLgUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=dfe7df34\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20181121/bkn-20181121111013931-1121_00952_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"23bba30c0e967157b4c66611c64ea7ba88b5689d","tid":910502,"uid":121580,"like":2,"dislike":25,"score":-23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T08:55:42.000Z","msg":"水份充足<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99084b2a74b0353c69dd1243f13568a460049c84","tid":910502,"uid":141869,"like":139,"dislike":0,"score":139,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T08:56:41.000Z","msg":"諗起整鵝肝啲鵝"},{"pid":"df87980433d49fa7484121274d18a7f60e2512a0","tid":910502,"uid":60686,"like":140,"dislike":1,"score":139,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T08:57:21.000Z","msg":"垃圾人種"},{"pid":"7b35f785a378335a258b20fb9df47581aac1a75a","tid":910502,"uid":81113,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T08:57:51.000Z","msg":"[今次好波]【01獨家】香港邊界失守　內地漁民空群越境　違禁漁具「蛇籠」竭澤而漁 禍害海洋<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/893802\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/893802</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e0e4a486037033d7a7ba58ca48716dcc01d83f32","tid":910502,"uid":78349,"like":165,"dislike":0,"score":165,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T08:59:01.000Z","msg":"祝老闆輪迴世世做中國牛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f71ce2fe26c018da556dd40007a6b488bbc67534","tid":910502,"uid":151926,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T08:59:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b15bb18f981113857614b5a6aaffefe99dd5b1bf","tid":910502,"uid":89868,"like":50,"dislike":35,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T08:59:50.000Z","msg":"得罪講句，唔少連登仔同佢諗法都一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d6fc293fa202797389143bce345dc87843350a2","tid":910502,"uid":108347,"like":92,"dislike":0,"score":92,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T09:01:48.000Z","msg":"最好捉班仆街灌水，放心唔會劏佢地咁衰嘅，嘔完痾完出黎再灌過，反正佢地遲早都死冇所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56b4f0f2d6e6f35d21f8b4a4fb27b0ec0e308925","tid":910502,"uid":2404,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T09:01:53.000Z","msg":"輕鬆啲就唔洗死咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"219e6a98275acbaf619ad6171decb8e4209ef53f","tid":910502,"uid":157362,"like":1,"dislike":49,"score":-48,"citedBy":8,"rep